# Gilam App

## Description
Gilam App is a mobile application developed for carpet washing companies to manage customer orders efficiently.  
The application allows companies to track orders, monitor their processing stages, and calculate income through a centralized system.

## Features
- Order creation and management
- Real-time order status tracking (current stage of each order)
- Display of total active orders
- Income calculation and financial tracking
- General statistics and analytics dashboard
- Fully online application with real-time data synchronization

## Technologies
- Unity Engine
- C#
- Firebase (Database & Authentication)
- Internet-based real-time data processing

## Functionality Overview
The application displays:
- How many orders are currently active
- The processing stage of each order
- Overall business statistics and revenue information

All data is stored in Firebase and synchronized in real time, ensuring reliable and up-to-date information across devices.

## How to Run
1. Clone the repository
2. Open the project using Unity Hub
3. Use the recommended Unity version
4. Configure Firebase settings
5. Run the application on an Android device or emulator

